PMID== 6968310
TI  == molecular characterization of "plasmid-free" antibiotic-resistant haemophilus influenzae.
AB  == we examined 14 multiresistant and 8 ampicillin- or tetracycline-resistant haemophilus influenzae isolates and 4 ampicillin-resistant h. parainfluenzae isolates for plasmid deoxyribonucleic acid. sixteen strains carried plasmids. both "plasmid-free" and plasmid-carrying isolates transferred the antibiotic resistance by conjugation. all transconjugants carried plasmid deoxyribonucleic acid, suggesting that the apparent plasmid-free strains contained r plasmids encoding for antibiotic resistance.
